Pangei da su praja mayam ama CRPF na yamna thina phubikhi, nupa macha amaga eikhoi mammagi machanupi amasu hatpikhi, maramdi CRPF 3 lom eikhoigi gyan takhraba naharol kharana CRPF ki Tata duda kapsil lubagi. Makhoina thouna phaba utpirubadagi emung kaya ama mentally traumatized oikhi, pakhang amaga leisaba mapung marei phadribido punsi lomkhi. Class 11 kagadabagi ming chaluba kuidribini, uniform turaga class 12 karani haiduna yamna haraokhibani enammado, naitom pokpi mamomloini. Mangjabadi chamjaraba emungsingni, nongmatasu lalle haina haibirakhide, makhoina wakhal khantharudabadagi thokhiba thoudokni. Nasanadi soidana khanglamgani, tanjaduda pangei da leiramba ema eben khudingmakse awaba takhibani, pelloko noi.   CRPF singdusu dandi phangdabida yamna nungaina lellamgani
